{
  "stem": "268.7",
  "chunk_idx": 13,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And he-- I says, it's April, isn't it?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "He says, yeah, it's April.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "The 9th, if you-- if you must know.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And I says, yeah, yeah, oh, the 9th.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "He said, when is your birthday?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Actually, my birthday wasn't until October.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "I says, well, I still got a few days' time.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "So we kept marching and marching.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And I said to myself, 9th of April.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "If-- if I live through tonight, I will celebrate my actual birthday that day.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And I, you know, silently started praying to God.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] I was thinking, what am I going to do?",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "[?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "I am ?] striped uniform.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "I have no papers, wooden shoes.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "I can hardly walk.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "Who-- if I do make a run for it, how am I going to hide?",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "Oh, what-- what's the difference?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "Tomorrow, the-- the Allieds-- either French or English or somebody will be here to liberate us.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "So just make a break for it.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "I know I can't-- I can't walk and I-- so I decided, I says to the other guys, I said, this village we're coming, we-- in the next one, I-- I'm-- I'm try to make a break.",
      "word_count": 37
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And he say, Henry, don't do this [? all the way. ?] Anyway, make a long story short, I-- they didn't want to come with me.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I said, fine, wish me luck.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So we-- we did a-- we came to the village square.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Some locals came out with buckets of water and ladles.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And they would let, like, five guys go and five come back.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And if you wanted to relieve yourself-- always in fives, you know-- they would count.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And sometimes they would-- they would be too tired to count already.",
      "word_count": 12
    }
  ],
